Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.58,0:00:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zanpakuto…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.45,0:00:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their shape and abilities are\Nbased on their Soul Reaper's soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.52,0:00:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soul Reapers gain power
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.99,0:00:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by learning their names\Nand synergizing with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.93,0:00:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are born with Soul Reapers\Nand die with Soul Reapers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.86,0:00:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is what Zanpakuto are.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.25,0:02:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This one's not the one, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.20,0:02:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.89,0:03:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.16,0:03:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You always turn your back\Ntowards reality!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.04,0:03:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Face reality!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.20,0:03:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you trying to say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.00,0:03:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were betrayed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.41,0:03:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the person you trusted most!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.00,0:03:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was by your side watching that,\Nunable to say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.41,0:03:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it really annoyed me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.85,0:03:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.12,0:03:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.28,0:03:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to destroy\Nyourself if this keeps up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.84,0:03:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I was by your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.04,0:03:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a thing to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.73,0:03:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what do you want to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.04,0:03:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to put you poor thing\Nto sleep forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.54,0:03:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.20,0:03:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.34,0:03:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot you've already been\Nasleep for quite some time now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.71,0:04:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does it hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.00,0:04:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. That's the pain of reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.58,0:04:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing like the naive world\Nyou believe it to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.50,0:04:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to make you\Ndiscard those ideas!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.20,0:04:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop being so overconfident,\Nold lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.70,0:04:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.68,0:04:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hinamori!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.09,0:04:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.29,0:04:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.20,0:04:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long are you going to\Nthink you're good looking?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.46,0:04:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Women have an expiration date.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.67,0:05:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you're past expiration.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.20,0:05:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.38,0:05:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough is enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.01,0:05:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try and make me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.49,0:05:17.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Owowowow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.93,0:05:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.99,0:05:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just trying to\Nhelp you look sexier.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.87,0:05:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course,\Nyou couldn't please anyone
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.58,0:05:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,since you're already expired.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.12,0:05:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps you shouldn't\Npush yourself, old lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.76,0:05:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.31,0:06:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's one more thing\NI want to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.88,0:06:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of the friends you trust\Nare just an illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.21,0:06:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just believe\Nthey're your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.00,0:06:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone just acts as if\Nthey're your friends
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.45,0:06:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because they have\Ntheir position to think of.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.94,0:06:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take Rangiku Matsumoto\Nthere for example…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.44,0:06:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing she's\Ninterested in is herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.69,0:06:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As proof, she's not paying\Nany attention to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.37,0:06:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you getting so upset?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.20,0:06:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you weren't an old lady,\Nyou wouldn't care!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.11,0:06:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really unsightly!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.04,0:06:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.59,0:06:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good bye, old lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.15,0:06:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who reigns!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.87,0:06:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mask of flesh and blood…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.60,0:07:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– All creation, the flutter of wings,\N– It's useless, useless,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.01,0:07:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– who crowns us names!\N– useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.34,0:07:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Disintegrate,\Nyou black dog of Rondanini!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.65,0:07:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– What are you trying to do?\N– Look upon yourself and burn!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.35,0:07:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tear out your own throat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.86,0:07:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bakudo 9! Horin!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.66,0:07:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think\Nyou're aiming at?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.20,0:07:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pay attention to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.25,0:07:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shakkaho!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.83,0:07:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you aiming?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.50,0:07:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old la—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.97,0:07:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bakudo 9! Horin!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.58,0:07:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.70,0:07:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey… What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.08,0:07:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't press yourself against me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.75,0:07:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not doing it because I want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.87,0:08:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.58,0:08:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it, Hinamori!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.00,0:08:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We sure did, Rangiku!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.37,0:08:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the meaning\Nof this, old lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.38,0:08:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me, that was all an act?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.85,0:08:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.62,0:08:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd never take a brat\Nlike you seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.41,0:08:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to go up against\Nyour Zanpakuto powers,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.56,0:08:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we needed to\Ncatch you off guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.63,0:08:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were only paying attention\Nto your own enemy,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.81,0:08:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so we were able to pull it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.28,0:08:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two suit each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.34,0:08:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to be kidding me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.14,0:08:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should try to\Nget along a little better.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.79,0:08:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.40,0:08:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But listening to you…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.41,0:08:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel sorry for you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.68,0:08:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.38,0:09:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You only think about yourself\Nand never think of others.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.27,0:09:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.75,0:09:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.61,0:09:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't pay any attention to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.63,0:09:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's just sore because\Nshe's an old lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.74,0:09:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit calling me an old lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.17,0:09:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.29,0:09:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to grow old.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.95,0:09:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.33,0:09:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being young isn't appealing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.48,0:09:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being young means that\Nyour heart is shallow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.60,0:09:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So whenever you admire\Nsomeone or you're betrayed,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.36,0:09:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you feel as if you're\Nflying or drowning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.62,0:09:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your emotions get\Nthe better of you
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.37,0:09:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and you lose sight of\Nwhere you belong.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.70,0:09:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Growing old means that\Nyour heart is gaining depth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.59,0:09:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're able to step away\Nfrom your wild emotions
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.54,0:09:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and keep those thoughts of\Nflying or sinking within you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.20,0:10:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what it means to grow old.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.33,0:10:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Expiration date" sounds shallow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.40,0:10:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't use it when referring\Nto a woman's age.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.55,0:10:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.12,0:10:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.41,0:10:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Children like you\Ncan't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.04,0:10:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah.\NThat's very admirable.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.97,0:10:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It's absurd, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.70,0:10:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what is it?\NWhy are you getting sulky?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.37,0:10:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my own business!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.08,0:10:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you just do\Nwhatever you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.45,0:10:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.67,0:10:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have no business\Ntelling me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.18,0:10:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, you're not cute at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.66,0:10:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.23,0:10:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your name is Hyorinmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.35,0:10:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I, Toshiro Hitsugaya,\Nam your master!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.64,0:11:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.48,0:11:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A child like you\Ncannot be my master.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.44,0:11:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.56,0:11:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've forgotten me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.10,0:11:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really think I'd\Nbelieve such nonsense, boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.60,0:11:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did that weird guy, Muramasa,\Ndo anything to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.10,0:11:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's none of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.56,0:11:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But when I was released\Nfrom my master,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.24,0:11:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost all of my memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.73,0:11:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of your memories?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.98,0:11:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now,\NI'm working for Muramasa,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.56,0:11:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but my goal is to find\Nmy true master.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.06,0:12:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your true master?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.96,0:12:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.40,0:12:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of my enormous power,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.52,0:12:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the person who uses me must be\Nthe most powerful Soul Reaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.15,0:12:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably not a child like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.56,0:12:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that my power\Nhasn't peaked…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.79,0:12:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that doesn't change\Nthe fact that I am your owner!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.51,0:12:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you insist on saying\Nthat you're my master,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.98,0:12:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then show me proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.55,0:12:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bakudo 63!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.29,0:12:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sajosabaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.33,0:13:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.94,0:13:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.56,0:13:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toshiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.32,0:13:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.95,0:13:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, Hyorinmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.22,0:13:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one you're fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.95,0:13:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hado 31!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.64,0:13:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shakkaho!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.48,0:13:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said it's useless.\NDon't you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.85,0:14:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zanpakuto…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.06,0:14:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear that the Zanpakuto were\Nreleased from the Soul Reapers
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.79,0:14:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to fulfill their desires.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.98,0:14:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case, Hyorinmaru,\Nwhat is your desire?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.22,0:14:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My desire?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.45,0:14:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Your desire.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.80,0:14:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does your soul want?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.91,0:14:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you forgotten even that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.06,0:15:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That would be…a place to\Ncall my own…a home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.44,0:15:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A home?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.99,0:15:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I might be searching for a home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.73,0:15:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A home… My home…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.31,0:15:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They're afraid of me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.12,0:15:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I haven't done anything.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.15,0:15:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But everyone is afraid of me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.92,0:15:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is it my silver hair?\NIs it my bluish green eyes?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.51,0:15:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Or is it my cold disposition?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.85,0:15:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm going to buy some amanatto.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.90,0:15:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're out of it, aren't you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.84,0:16:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Grandma has gotten pretty thin.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.15,0:16:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Grandma began getting thin\Nwhen I began to have those dreams.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.28,0:16:09.28,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sweets{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.05,0:16:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Your change is 3 kan.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.56,0:16:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thanks.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.24,0:16:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If that's all you want,\Nthen get going.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.52,0:16:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.10,0:16:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's no way to treat a customer!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.52,0:16:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Are you going to disregard him\Njust because he's a child?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.09,0:16:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I had no idea this shop\Nlacked common courtesy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.86,0:16:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh… N-No…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.11,0:16:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How long are you going to cry?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.23,0:16:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you're a man, then give him\Na piece of your mind!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.41,0:16:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whose fault do you think this is?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.99,0:16:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And I'm not crying! Let go of me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.65,0:16:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I said, let go!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.77,0:16:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh! Hey!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.85,0:16:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.31,0:16:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That dream…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.20,0:17:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I hear a voice.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.05,0:17:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's echoing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.66,0:17:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It feels like it's crushing me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.52,0:17:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It feels like it's surrounding me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.27,0:17:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It feels like lightning is\Ncoming down on my hand.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.41,0:17:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who the hell are you?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.00,0:17:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Boy! You are my…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.45,0:17:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What are you saying?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.67,0:17:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't hear you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.70,0:17:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My name is…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.75,0:17:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't hear you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.83,0:17:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.11,0:17:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're the lady\NI met earlier today.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.73,0:17:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shut off your Spiritual Pressure\Nwhen you sleep.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.76,0:17:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Your grandmother seems cold.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.16,0:17:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gr—{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.00,0:17:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Become a Soul Reaper, boy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.20,0:17:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.51,0:17:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A strong kid like you needs to\Nlearn how to control your power.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.80,0:17:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let me tell you this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.64,0:18:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you continue on like this,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.12,0:18:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}your power is going to\Nkill your grandmother.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.58,0:18:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What are you saying?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.29,0:18:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You can hear a voice, can't you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.25,0:18:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rein Over\Nthe Frosted Heavens…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.95,0:18:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hyorinmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.00,0:18:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can use my power?\NBoy… How?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.59,0:18:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You still can't remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.50,0:18:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let me show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.46,0:19:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what'll happen if I\Nuse this attack in Shikai, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.08,0:19:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryusenka!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.50,0:19:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Getsugatensho!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.27,0:19:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toshiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.00,0:19:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.81,0:19:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember the person\Nwho heard your voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.16,0:19:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember your home!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.66,0:19:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Boy… Are you\Ngoing to wield me?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.89,0:20:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My name is…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.37,0:20:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My name is…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.62,0:20:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hyorinmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.62,0:20:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.83,0:20:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You remembered.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.07,0:20:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But my name's not "boy."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.83,0:20:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Toshiro Hitsugaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.05,0:21:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.16,0:21:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll have to do for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.04,0:23:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.00,0:23:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please let me borrow\NHyorinmaru just this once!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.85,0:23:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always wanted to
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.96,0:23:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,walk a handsome man\Non a leash as my pet!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.32,0:23:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.06,0:23:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let you borrow\NHaieko in exchange!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.95,0:23:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.76,0:23:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are, like, totally annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.27,0:23:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Absolutely not!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.06,0:23:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Illustrated Guide to Soul Reapers!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.67,0:23:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.23,0:23:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you solve the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.83,0:23:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! I'm through detention!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.41,0:23:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?!\NSis isn't even here!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.84,0:23:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was planning to spend\Nsome time in paradise!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.18,0:23:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you have against me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.83,0:23:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If anything…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.30,0:24:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your body is a Soul Reaper and\NSoul Reapers are my enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.15,0:24:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still saying that?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.09,0:24:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,